// Copy to `.dev.vars` for local `wrangler dev`. In production set these as
// secrets with `wrangler secret put <NAME>`.

// A2A_SIGNING_KEY: an Ed25519 private JWK (one line) that signs this agent's
// AgentCard. MUST include a `kid`. Generate with `npm run keygen`.
// Only the matching PUBLIC key is ever exposed, at /.well-known/jwks.json.
A2A_SIGNING_KEY=

// GATEWAY_ORIGINS: JSON array of trusted gateway origins, e.g.
// ["https://gw.example.com"]. Must match the deployed gateway's own
// GATEWAY_ORIGIN. Not a traditional secret, but kept out of wrangler.jsonc
// for deploy-time convenience (differs per environment, no code change to ship).
GATEWAY_ORIGINS=
